item.title: CVE-2023-3935|2024-08-02T07:08:50.775Z -- wibu -- codemeter%20runtime
item.description: A heap buffer overflow vulnerability in Wibu CodeMeter Runtime network service up to version 7.60b allows an unauthenticated, remote attacker to achieve RCE and gain full access of the host system.
